# NebulaGuard

NebulaGuard is a modern file monitoring and backup utility written in Python.

## Features

- Monitor directories in real-time
- Automatic versioned backups
- Duplicate file detection
- Restore previous file versions
- HTML & JSON reports
- Cross-platform support

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/NebulaGuard.git

cd NebulaGuard
pip install -r requirements.txt
python nebulaguard.py --watch ./Documents
[INFO] Monitoring: ./Documents
[INFO] File modified: report.docx
[BACKUP] Version saved.
[REPORT] report.html generated.

cd NebulaGuard
pip install -r requirements.txt
python nebulaguard.py --watch ./Doc
---

